name: go-apicurio-registry
description: go-apicurio-registry is an open-source Go SDK for Apicurio Schema Registry v3.0 APIs. It offers an idiomatic Go interface to manage schemas, validate data, and handle schema evolution in Go applications. Perfect for integrating Apicurio into Go-based microservices or event-driven systems.
